normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n羅清你無論後門定正門都係咁勁"},{"pid":"cfd8ff09635bab4a16c465a92cde7a4f2fc98eae","tid":799262,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T08:46:53.000Z","msg":"補充資料 1：<br />\n<br />\n大學教育資助委員會（<span style=\"color: blue;\">教資會</span>）University Grants Committee (<span style=\"color: blue;\">UGC</span>) 旗下有八間大學（<span style=\"color: blue;\">八大</span>）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XvYe59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXvYe59&h=1f0468e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VNvPLw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVNvPLw&h=63a58961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中本身<ins>一成立就已經係大學嘅大學</ins>只有 <span style=\"color: blue;\">HKUST 香港科技大學</span>，其餘七大院校論獲得／有「大學」頭銜嘅歷史倒時序如下：<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1881 年：<ins>官立師範學堂 Government Normal School</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1939 年：<ins>羅富國師範學院 Northcote Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/EvNTGR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEvNTGR&h=40e17823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>葛量洪師範學院 Grantham Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ezdGkn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FezdGkn&h=c5fc7c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1960 年：<ins>柏立基師範學院 Sir Robert Black Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/RCcEyv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FRCcEyv&h=12ccbd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1967 年：三所師範學院易名為<ins>教育學院 Colleges of Education</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1974 年：<ins>香港工商師範學院 Hong Kong Technical Teachers' College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VqcZuB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVqcZuB&h=c0f18adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1982 年：<ins>語文教育學院 Institute of Language in Education</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FqDDTv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFqDDTv&h=dc1fc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1994 年：五所師訓學院合併為 <strong><ins>HKIEd 香港教育學院 (The Hong Kong Institute of Education)</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/nMVUzd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnMVUzd&h=8b7ef130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EdUHK 香港教育大學 (The Education University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/vCdavY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FvCdavY&h=ee4a3fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1888 年：<ins>格致書院</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1903 年：<ins>嶺南學堂</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1912 年：<ins>嶺南學校</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- <strong><ins>1927-1952 年</ins></strong>：<strong><ins>嶺南大學</ins></strong>（廣州）<br />\n- 1967 年：<ins>嶺南書院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/zgSkFR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzgSkFR&h=cf3d2753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 1978 年：<ins>嶺南學院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jeNgV4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjeNgV4&h=2ebe6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1999 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LU 嶺南大學 (Lingnan University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jyxiWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjyxiWg&h=10cb3cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1937 年：<ins>香港官立高級工業學院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XzYfmH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXzYfmH&h=15df4cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1947 年：<ins>香港工業專門學院 Hong Kong Technical College (HKTC)</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/mbJhbW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmbJhbW&h=3831d4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/muYqzQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmuYqzQ&h=495bba67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：<ins>香港理工學院 Hong Kong Polytechnic</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/MwMofP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FMwMofP&h=3e6ef969&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/Z9za5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZ9za5V&h=c7ce1665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">PolyU 香港理工大學 (The Hong Kong Polytechnic University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/fKwYmk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfKwYmk&h=6262f338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1984 年：香港第二所理工學院<ins>「香港城市理工學院」City Polytechnic of Hong Kong</ins> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/AxmUQ3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAxmUQ3&h=51b439fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">CityU 香港城市大學 (City University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/TbByx8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTbByx8&h=08d3556c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 2015 年：起用新校徽 logo<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/APKnhz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAPKnhz&h=f3da7696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1956 年：<ins>香港浸會書院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/gbktgn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fgbktgn&h=f50296c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：改稱<ins>香港浸會學院 Hong Kong Baptist College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ACbAJ4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FACbAJ4&h=6dfbd898&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/F9QYvP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FF9QYvP&h=929132e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKBU 香港浸會大學 (Hong Kong Baptist University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/aFkVTK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FaFkVTK&h=c02dba86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1991 年</span></span>：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKUST 香港科技大學 (The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/LEAwFT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FLEAwFT&h=887bebfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1949 年：<ins>新亞書院 New Asia College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/WxZn5K\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWxZn5K&h=4f2e374a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>崇基學院 Chung Chi College</ins>（由民國大陸時期十三間基督教大學遷到香港組成）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ZKUm8U\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZKUm8U&h=8da962d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1956 年：<ins>聯合書院 United College of Hong Kong</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/bcNSdS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbcNSdS&h=b1f2aa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1963 年</span></span>：三院合併，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">CUHK 香港中文大學 (The Chinese University of Hong Kong)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/p3ptNx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fp3ptNx&h=7855c725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1887 年：<ins>香港華人西醫書院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/x1igvm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fx1igvm&h=003a9f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1906 年：<ins>香港工學院</ins><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1912 年</span></span>：增設<ins>文學院</ins>，三院組成 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKU 香港大學 (The University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FnJEnJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFnJEnJ&h=b38ba950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝"},{"pid":"90efe6db2fefce754b3e6481d83edd7ea42ee69c","tid":799262,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">UGC 八大</span>以外：</span><br />\n<br />\n- 1989 年：<ins>香港公開進修學院 Open Learning Institute of Hong Kong</ins> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/U3kWDt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FU3kWDt&h=54b4187c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1996 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">OUHK 香港公開大學 (The Open University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/927kLE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F927kLE&h=cd63fa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n- 1971 年：<ins>香港樹仁書院</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1976 年：<ins>香港樹仁學院 Hong Kong Shun Yan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/dMuwSp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdMuwSp&h=b9cb712f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2006 年</span></span>：正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKSYU 香港樹仁大學 (Hong Kong Shue Yan University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/sTVBnU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FsTVBnU&h=7621e2b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/8HdgNc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8HdgNc&h=7deef38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n補充資料 2：<br />\n香港其實有<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">二十一大</span></span>（如果計 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">QF level 5 degree-awarding 學士學位</span></span>）<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fedu-system%2Fpostsecondary%2Flocal-higher-edu%2Finstitutions%2Findex.html&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c2524194\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/local-higher-edu/institutions/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n不過<strong><ins>資助</ins></strong>得 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">UGC 八大</span></span> + <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公帑資助 HK